{"tid":793574,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］火影忍者影分身之極限操作","createTime":"2018-08-25T13:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:08:21.000Z","uid":6521,"like":33,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2294e9fbd6c112c0738655ce7c208c146b4b683d","tid":793574,"uid":6521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過如果你識影分身可以點樣令呢種忍術發揮到最大威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你可以用影分身自己含自己<br />\n<br />\n你勁啲的話仲可以用色誘術，中出任何靚女，只要你想像到佢個樣，你就可以用影分身色誘自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最大隱憂就係，影分身係會有自己意識，每當影分身消失，佢經歷過嘅事就會浮現係你腦海，即刻共享經驗。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，你體驗到口爆，中出之餘，你都會體驗埋被口爆同被中出，仲要係自己中出自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係咁，你哋仲會唔會咁樣使用影分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用左手打番丁都唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/215842_116c588613d21ebc80f9f356645dc15f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F215842_116c588613d21ebc80f9f356645dc15f.png&h=9ec492f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eac2542c68b3b6a021e35d336f0e0fdc1c30582","tid":793574,"uid":60412,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"用影分身瘋狂返工ot"},{"pid":"0d25f9337364ef9f9a708fb4200b2f4b7aaa0ea9","tid":793574,"uid":6521,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"1eac2542c68b3b6a021e35d336f0e0fdc1c30582","tid":793574,"uid":60412,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"用影分身瘋狂返工ot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"當你個影分身用盡查克拉個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你會有嚴重抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247ee8b218259a3a8e9c57a507e3a6c32abc0579","tid":793574,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:09:49.000Z","msg":"賣藝表演做show<br />\n搵到錢就咩都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4dd0312d387d4d8b61d1da4de5bb48ea5d1b8b","tid":793574,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"一定用影分身返工供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fb2548c163c4df425aa7dcd4f35916441745ee","tid":793574,"uid":6521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a4dd0312d387d4d8b61d1da4de5bb48ea5d1b8b","tid":793574,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"一定用影分身返工供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"香港人輕鬆啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奴性唔好咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c74bf1c081350b26d210ab6899aa64a5d38d3a","tid":793574,"uid":176837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"整幾個分身去打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己再係求其搵一間警局面前企 製造不在場證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c453fa9120b5336cc5fe73a5576862a953d582ee","tid":793574,"uid":161230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"影分身最大特點係可以累積學習經驗，所以最好應該係做一啲要經驗累積嘅工作"},{"pid":"8e7a39ec22ca5e436c252966115c20d2c92c4c54","tid":793574,"uid":6521,"like":3,"